# Copy to .env only if you need to override (e.g. Expo --tunnel hides LAN IP, or API on another host).
# With Expo Go on the same Wi-Fi as your PC, the app picks your dev machine IP from Expo automatically.
# API must listen on all interfaces (launch profile uses http://0.0.0.0:5048) and Windows Firewall may need port 5048 allowed.
#
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://192.168.1.10:5048
